snippet.title: Space Invaders '95 - Arcade- Space Invaders Games (Taito 1995)
snippet.description:
Space Invaders '95 - arcade. As one of the Space Invaders Games that followed the wake of the original blockbuster arcade game, you gotta say at least they did something different here. Subtitled: The Attack of the Lunar Loonies. A one world description: Insanity

March lockstep along with the history of Space Invaders, at The Dot Eaters: 
http://thedoteaters.com/?bitstory=bitstory-article-2/space-invaders

http://www.thedoteaters.com  Video Game History 101
